OL,3,CMotorhead guitarist Phil Campbell dies
OL,4,Caged 64
OL,6,FFormer Motorhead guitarist Phil
OL,7,FCampbell has died, aged 64.
OL,9,FIn a family tribute made on Facebook,
OL,10,Fhe was described as a "devoted
OL,11,Fhusband" and a "wonderful father."
OL,13,FThe Welsh musician, born in
OL,14,FPontypridd, was part of the iconic
OL,15,Frock band for over 30 years, joining
OL,16,Fin 1984 and remaining alongside
OL,17,Ffrontman Ian "Lemmy" Kilmister until
OL,18,Fthe group's dissolution following
OL,19,FLemmy's death in 2015.
OL,26,@kD@DxwnD@Kxw
