OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F468A1773765951
OL,3,CMotorhead guitarist Phil Campbell dies
OL,4,Caged 64
OL,6,FThe family confirmed that Campbell
OL,7,Fpassed away "peacefully" on Friday 14,
OL,8,FMarch following a period of ill health.
OL,10,F"It is with great sadness that we
OL,11,Fannounce the passing of our beloved
OL,12,Ffather, Philip Anthony Campbell, who
OL,13,Fpassed away peacefully last night
OL,14,Ffollowing a long and courageous battle
OL,15,Fin intensive care after a complex
OL,16,Fmajor operation," the statement read.
OL,26,@kD@Dxw
