OL,3,CMotorhead guitarist Phil Campbell dies
OL,4,Caged 64
OL,6,FThe family also touched on his
OL,7,Fpersonal life away from the world of
OL,8,Fheavy metal, in his role as a "proud
OL,9,Fand loving grandfather, known
OL,10,Faffectionately as 'Bampi.'"
OL,12,F"He was deeply loved by all who knew
OL,13,Fhim and will be missed immensely. His
OL,14,Flegacy, music and the memories he
OL,15,Fcreated with so many will live on
OL,16,Fforever."
OL,26,@kD@Dxw
