OL,3,CMotorhead guitarist Phil Campbell dies
OL,4,Caged 64
OL,6,FIn a previous interview with ITV
OL,7,FWales' Backstage programme, he said he
OL,8,Fhad "too many" memorable moment's
OL,9,Fthroughout his time with the band, but
OL,10,Fthat winning a Grammy Award "was
OL,11,Fpretty cool".
OL,13,FCampbell then went on tour with his
OL,14,Fown band, alongside his three sons,
OL,15,Fwhich was formed two years before
OL,16,FMotorhead came to an end.
OL,26,@kD@DxwxD@Dxw
