OL,3,CMotorhead guitarist Phil Campbell dies
OL,4,Caged 64
OL,6,FPrevious he said: "I have to pinch
OL,7,Fmyself sometimes, the music is so hot
OL,8,Fand firing up great on stage, and then
OL,9,FI think oh my god my kids are on the
OL,10,Fother side."
OL,12,FThe family has requested that their
OL,13,Fprivacy is respected during this
OL,14,F"incredibly difficult time."
